<h2>Welcome to <%= appName || 'FAQ Manager' %>! 🎉</h2>

<p>Hi<% if (typeof userName !== 'undefined' && userName) { %> <strong><%= userName %></strong><% } %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for creating your account. We're excited to have you on board!</p>

<p>With <%= appName || 'FAQ Manager' %>, you can:</p>

<ul style="margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 24px;">
  <li>Create and manage FAQs for your Shopify store</li>
  <li>Enable community Q&A with customer questions and answers</li>
  <li>Moderate content with flexible publishing rules</li>
  <li>Track engagement with built-in analytics</li>
  <li>Embed a beautiful FAQ widget on your storefront</li>
</ul>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a>
</p>

<hr class="divider">

<h3 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Getting Started</h3>

<p>Here's how to set up your FAQ system:</p>

<ol style="margin: 16px 0; padding-left: 24px; color: #4b5563;">
  <li><strong>Add your Shopify credentials</strong> — Connect your store in the Credentials page</li>
  <li><strong>Create categories</strong> — Organize your FAQs by topic</li>
  <li><strong>Add your first FAQ</strong> — Start building your knowledge base</li>
  <li><strong>Install the widget</strong> — Copy the embed code to your theme</li>
</ol>

<% if (typeof verifyEmailUrl !== 'undefined' && verifyEmailUrl) { %>
<div class="alert-box alert-info">
  <strong>Verify your email</strong><br>
  Please verify your email address to unlock all features.
  <br><br>
  <a href="<%= verifyEmailUrl %>" class="btn" style="margin: 0;">Verify Email</a>
</div>
<% } %>

<p class="muted">If you have any questions, just reply to this email — we're here to help!</p>
